data.description: Welcome to this well maintained home in the Spring Creek subdivision. Come relax by the fireplace, in your one of two living areas. Cook in a spacious kitchen, which features an island and plenty of space for storage, and choose to eat either in your breakfast nook, or in your formal dining room. Retreat to the master suite which is separated from the other three bedrooms, or find peace in your backyard as you sit on your deck, or take a dip in your personal pool! This home features everything you need whether you are one to entertain, or are just looking for more space, and is conveniently located to highways, shopping centers, and schools.
